<h2>You know, I often see images that are a bit unclear and which may sometimes mean more to you than to me.</h2>
<h3>If you help, we can together uncover new things about you...</h3>
<br>
<p>I think I have seen you in the crystal ball, but it is all very vague... <br>
	Why don't you tell me your name and email?</p>

<%= render 'form' %>
<button id='showemail' class='btn'>I googled some emails for your testing pleasure:</button>
<button id='show5k' class='emails btn info' style='display:none'>5,000 emails</button>
<button id='show10k' class='emails btn' style='display:none'>10,000 emails</button>


<script>
	$('#showemail').click(function(){
		$(this).hide();
		$('.emails').show();
	});
	$('#show5k').click(function(){
		$('#5k').toggle();
		$('#10k').toggle();
		$('#show5k').addClass('info');
		$('#show10k').removeClass('info');	
	});
	$('#show10k').click(function(){
		$('#10k').toggle();
		$('#5k').toggle();
		$('#show5k').removeClass('info');
		$('#show10k').addClass('info');
		
	});
	$('.field_with_errors').css('display','inline')
</script>
<%= link_to 'Back', consultings_path %>
<div class='emails' style='display:none;'>
	<textarea id='5k' style='width:350px;'><%=IO.read('shortermailinglist.txt').strip.html_safe %></textarea>
	<textarea id='10k' style='display:none; width:350px;'><%=IO.read('shortmailinglist.txt').strip.html_safe %></textarea>
</div>
